wiki.content: Despite controversial media coverage recently, sales of Amy's album 'Back to Black' have continued to grow and grow. Fourth single 'Tears Dry On Their Own' followed 'Rehab', 'You Know I'm No Good' and the title track in the top 30. wiki.summary: Despite controversial media coverage recently, sales of Amy's album 'Back to Black' have continued to grow and grow. Fourth single 'Tears Dry On Their Own' followed 'Rehab', 'You Know I'm No Good' and the title track in the top 30.
